title: Episode 269: Defeating Bowser (Feat. LightSkinKeisha)
itunes:title: Episode 269: Defeating Bowser (Feat. LightSkinKeisha)
description:
LightSkinKeisha gets graphic when confessing to having phone sex with her boyfriend, opens up about friends getting jealous when she fell in love, and much more. LightSkinKeisha even gets vulnerable when speaking on topics such as overcoming homelessness, as well as being depressed while being signed to a label. Enjoy!
